snippet.title: Flip the Gun - Simulator Game
snippet.description:
Enjoy brand-new realistic physics game: make weapons fly using their recoil. Shoot and fly as high as possible!
 
Ultra-realistic physics game, where you can try yourself in shooting. Shoot wisely with AWP and pistols, make fantastic burst with automatic weapons or blow it up with bazooka!
 
— 15 cool physics-based weapons
— unique game mechanics
— shoot using weapons from your favorite games and movies
 
Unlock and try all amazing weapons and make your gun reach the worldwide high score!
